            <lg xml:id="TK152">
<l>poṟutta liṟappiṉai yeṉṟu mataṉai</l>
<l>maṟatta lataṉiṉu naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To tolerate transgression is always good;</l>
<l>to forget is even better.</l>
